'''''Cr'ee'ei''''' was the [[Lwhekk-class manufacturing ship|''Lwhekk''-class manufacturing ship]] assigned to the first [[Ssi-ruu]]vi fleet that attacked [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura]]. Its name roughly translates into "Maker Ship".<ref name="TaBSB">''[[The Truce at Bakura Sourcebook]]''</ref>

Although ships of its class were capable of holding up to 2,000 [[Swarm-class battle droid|''Swarm''-class battle droids]], ''Cr'ee'ei'' was depleted of droid starfighters by the time of the [[Invasion of Bakura|Bakura invasion]]. It would not have been able to produce more battle droids until Bakura's raw materials were seized. Following convention, the lightly-armed ''Cr'ee'ei'' stayed behind the main Ssi-ruuvi fleet, never actually entering the battle. It retreated along with the remaining Ssi-ruuvi ships after the [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] [[Sibwarra|''Shriwirr'']] was captured by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]].

